{"tid":1034602,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"渡邊麻友裸身女女共浴　3次激吻強佔豐唇","createTime":"2019-02-24T04:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T13:56:14.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8cac22c2c303450a4792ca4aa40089b84be01a43","tid":1034602,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"▲澤尻英龍華主演《大奧》，和渡邊麻友展開禁忌女女戀。（圖／翻攝自日網《富士電視台》）<br />\n<br />\n記者陳芊秀／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n日本女星澤尻英龍華擁有甜美臉蛋，作風卻十分大膽，接演古裝劇《大奧》系列，描述江戶時代將軍後宮爭鬥，分上下兩集播出，尤其是搭檔AKB48成員之一的渡邊麻友，2人上演女女臉，引起觀眾注目。電視劇於22日晚間播出第一部，她不但脫衣入浴，和渡邊麻友熱吻多達3次，激情畫面掀起討論。<br />\n<br />\n《大奧》的故事題材和港劇《金枝慾孽》、陸劇《後宮甄嬛傳》相似，皆是描述在治理天下的王者背後，後宮3千佳麗爭寵、互鬥的人生，澤尻英龍華在故事中扮演將軍側室「美代」，並有許多入浴場面。不過，最令人關注的，是她在故事中邂逅對男人無感的渡邊麻友，儘管受到將軍寵愛，仍陷入禁忌的女女戀，尤其她托起對方下巴，啃咬女方豐唇狂洩愛慾，畫面直叫觀眾看了心跳加速。<br />\n<br />\n▲▼澤尻英龍華和渡邊麻友激吻3次，還一起裸身入浴，挑戰電視尺度。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渡邊麻友22日 在「AKB48熱門金曲票選」活動中，和現場粉絲分享拍攝《大奧》的秘辛，眾成員好奇她和澤尻英龍華的激烈吻戲，她表示拍庭院吻戲當天，是第一次和對方見面，也是雙方第一場戲，2人才剛打完招呼，就要拍激吻戲，忍不住臉羞紅說：「我心臟撲通撲通跳好快啊！」"},{"pid":"05465cbaa409d4826907dbbff5f730e61cf8b763","tid":1034602,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"@賓科<br />\n@卡奴"},{"pid":"be20598610b144001aedfdb449b5a10b82aef215","tid":1034602,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"共浴呢啲佢做慣哂"},{"pid":"9c09dd5fbb22b6629745772b0cdc491acdc9eb0b","tid":1034602,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"bde09bfaf12be67fc32187308f896a77c3ef02ef","tid":1034602,"uid":2474,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab031f3316d2fd2bce3122ffbcc914b20fa8ea4e","tid":1034602,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be20598610b144001aedfdb449b5a10b82aef215","tid":1034602,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"共浴呢啲佢做慣哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"水中蕭"},{"pid":"a31ef037bdb880375626d2945998c2c32d7a5366","tid":1034602,"uid":206388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:59:40.000Z","msg":"又冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eabbf537b2f6b973c15f78712b93f898bf574a1","tid":1034602,"uid":12000,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T06:54:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/7Um0zkY.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Um0zkY.png&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=627c5ff0\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/7Um0zkY.png</a>"},{"pid":"4632d93f8b19c609689cc30546be72231d6a8033","tid":1034602,"uid":1426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T06:56:06.000Z","msg":"G,無波點波推"},{"pid":"c36101cab4133eb457f9f0d77d479d58de3cd687","tid":1034602,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"172fc83cda91bbfd1daf602d73f2e7c7c71bc8e4","tid":1034602,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/static.ettoday.net/images/1568/d1568474.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1568%2Fd1568474.jpg&h=fd0eae0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fa216f6c1adcce78f776da6e29f7be8eda3226e","tid":1034602,"uid":69115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"老雞.jpg"}]}